title: Gallup ‘Most Admired Man’ Poll Not Indicative of Electoral Fraud
subtitle: Future White House occupants have figured prominently — but not consistently — when Gallup has asked Americans to name the man they admire most.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: Joe Biden's low ranking in a 2020 Gallup 'Most Admired Man' poll is an anomalous result indicative of electoral fraud.
